        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="在脚本中使用GameObject"><a href="#在脚本中使用GameObject" class="headerlink" title="在脚本中使用GameObject"></a>在脚本中使用GameObject</h1><p>在物体上挂载组件后，编辑脚本<br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/03/09/cQBbk26g5mjMtKZ.png" alt="脚本组件.PNG"></p><pre><code>// 获取当前脚本的物体的名称等信息</code></pre><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//GameObject go = this.gameObject;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//名称</span></span><br><span class="line">Debug.Log(gameObject.name);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//标签</span></span><br><span class="line">Debug.Log(gameObject.tag);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在配置好实体和预设体后</p><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//获取实体</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> GameObject Cube;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">//获取预设体</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> GameObject Prefab;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//获取内部的方块，并查询激活状态</span></span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(Cube.name);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//真正状态</span></span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(Cube.activeInHierarchy);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//勾选栏状态</span></span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(Cube.activeSelf);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//获取Trancform组件</span></span><br><span class="line">       Transform t = <span class="keyword">this</span>.transform;</span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(transform.position);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//获取其他组件</span></span><br><span class="line">       BoxCollider bc = GetComponent&lt;BoxCollider&gt;();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//通过物体名字和标签获取物体对象</span></span><br><span class="line">       GameObject test = GameObject.Find(<span class="string">&quot;Test&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">       test = GameObject.FindWithTag(<span class="string">&quot;Enemy&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(test.name);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//预设体实例化一个物体</span></span><br><span class=